---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import FooterSignature from '../components/FooterSignature.astro';
import LangToggle from '../components/LangToggle.astro';
---

<Layout title="Datenschutzerklärung — postctl">
  <!-- Background Glows -->
  <div class="bg-glow bg-glow-1"></div>
  <div class="bg-glow bg-glow-2"></div>
  <div class="grid-overlay"></div>

  <!-- Minimal Header -->
  <header class="tui-page-header">
    <a href="/" class="tui-logo">
      <span class="logo-icon">&gt;_</span>
      <span class="logo-text">postctl<span class="logo-blink">_</span></span>
    </a>
    <div class="tui-page-header-right">
      <a href="/" class="back-link"><span class="lang-en">← Back to Home</span><span class="lang-de">← Zurück zur Startseite</span></a>
      <button id="lang-toggle" class="lang-toggle-btn" aria-label="Toggle Language">
        <span class="lang-en">DE</span>
        <span class="lang-de">EN</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="tui-page-main">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="tui-page-section-header">
      <div class="section-tag"><span class="lang-en">Security</span><span class="lang-de">Sicherheit</span></div>
      <h1 class="section-title"><span class="lang-en">Privacy Policy</span><span class="lang-de">Datenschutzerklärung</span></h1>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        <span class="lang-en">Information on the processing of personal data under the EU GDPR.</span>
        <span class="lang-de">Informationen über die Verarbeitung personenbezogener Daten gemäß EU-DSGVO.</span>
      </p>
      <p class="lang-note">
        <span class="lang-en">This English version is a courtesy translation. The German version is legally binding.</span>
        <span class="lang-de">Diese englische Version ist eine Übersetzung zur Information. Maßgeblich ist die deutsche Fassung.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Privacy Stack Layout -->
    <div class="privacy-stack">
      <!-- Section 1 -->
      <div class="privacy-card">
        <div class="card-label">// 01_PRIVACY_OVERVIEW</div>
        <h3 class="card-title"><span class="lang-en">Privacy at a Glance</span><span class="lang-de">Datenschutz auf einen Blick</span></h3>
        <p class="card-text">
          <span class="lang-en">
            We place the greatest importance on protecting your privacy. postctl is designed as a <strong>local-first</strong> application.
            This means your data (such as passwords, API keys, session cookies, and post data) is stored locally on your machine in an
            encrypted SQLite database and is never transmitted to us.
          </span>
          <span class="lang-de">
            Wir legen größten Wert auf den Schutz deiner Privatsphäre. postctl ist als <strong>local-first</strong> Anwendung konzipiert.
            Das bedeutet, dass deine Daten (wie Passwörter, API-Keys, Session-Cookies und Beitragsdaten) lokal auf deinem Rechner in einer
            SQLite-Datenbank verschlüsselt gespeichert werden und zu keinem Zeitpunkt an uns übertragen werden.
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 2 -->
      <div class="privacy-card">
        <div class="card-label">// 02_DESKTOP_CLIENT_DATA</div>
        <h3 class="card-title"><span class="lang-en">Data Collection in the App (Desktop Client)</span><span class="lang-de">Datenerfassung in der App (Desktop-Client)</span></h3>
        <p class="card-text">
          <span class="lang-en">The app stores login credentials and tokens for connected social media accounts (e.g. LinkedIn, Threads, Twitter/X) exclusively locally on the user's device using AES-256-GCM encryption.</span>
          <span class="lang-de">Die App speichert Anmeldedaten und Tokens für verbundene Social-Media-Accounts (z. B. LinkedIn, Threads, Twitter/X) ausschließlich lokal auf dem Gerät des Benutzers unter Verwendung von AES-256-GCM Verschlüsselung.</span>
        </p>
        <p class="card-text">
          <span class="lang-en">There is no central cloud database, no trackers, no telemetry, and no server logs on our part. Your data belongs exclusively to you.</span>
          <span class="lang-de">Es gibt keine zentrale Cloud-Datenbank, keine Tracker, keine Telemetrie und keine Serverprotokolle unsererseits. Deine Daten gehören ausschließlich dir.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 3 -->
      <div class="privacy-card">
        <div class="card-label">// 03_MERCHANT_OF_RECORD</div>
        <h3 class="card-title"><span class="lang-en">Payment Processing & Licensing (Polar.sh)</span><span class="lang-de">Zahlungsabwicklung & Lizenzierung (Polar.sh)</span></h3>
        <p class="card-text">
          <span class="lang-en">
            If you purchase a postctl Pro license, payment processing and license key generation are handled via the external service
            <strong>Polar.sh</strong> (Polar Technologies Inc.). Polar acts as the "Merchant of Record".
          </span>
          <span class="lang-de">
            Wenn du eine Pro-Lizenz von postctl erwirbst, wird die Zahlungsabwicklung und Lizenzschlüssel-Generierung über den externen Dienst
            <strong>Polar.sh</strong> (Polar Technologies Inc.) abgewickelt. Polar agiert als „Merchant of Record“.
          </span>
        </p>
        <p class="card-text">
          <span class="lang-en">
            In doing so, personal data such as your e-mail address and billing information is collected in order to issue the license and
            fulfil tax obligations. Further information can be found in Polar.sh's privacy policy at
            <a href="https://polar.sh/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="accent-link underline">https://polar.sh/privacy</a>.
          </span>
          <span class="lang-de">
            Dabei werden personenbezogene Daten wie E-Mail-Adresse und Rechnungsdaten erfasst, um die Lizenz auszustellen und steuerliche
            Pflichten zu erfüllen. Weitere Informationen findest du in der Datenschutzerklärung von Polar.sh unter
            <a href="https://polar.sh/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="accent-link underline">https://polar.sh/privacy</a>.
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 4 -->
      <div class="privacy-card">
        <div class="card-label">// 04_WEB_HOSTING_LOGS</div>
        <h3 class="card-title"><span class="lang-en">Website Hosting</span><span class="lang-de">Hosting der Website</span></h3>
        <p class="card-text">
          <span class="lang-en">
            This website is hosted on GitHub Pages / Cloudflare. When you visit this website, IP addresses and connection logs are
            collected by default to ensure the stability and security of the website. This constitutes a legitimate interest under
            Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR.
          </span>
          <span class="lang-de">
            Diese Website wird gehostet auf GitHub Pages / Cloudflare. Beim Aufrufen dieser Website werden standardmäßig IP-Adressen und
            Verbindungsprotokolle erhoben, um die Stabilität und Sicherheit der Website zu gewährleisten. Dies ist ein berechtigtes Interesse
            gemäß Art. 6 Abs. 1 lit. f DSGVO.
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 5 -->
      <div class="privacy-card">
        <div class="card-label">// 05_USER_RIGHTS</div>
        <h3 class="card-title"><span class="lang-en">Your Rights (GDPR)</span><span class="lang-de">Deine Rechte (DSGVO)</span></h3>
        <p class="card-text">
          <span class="lang-en">
            Regarding your data collected via Polar.sh or through our servers, you generally have the rights to access, rectification,
            erasure, restriction, data portability, and to withdraw consent or object. Please contact the e-mail address given in the
            legal notice for this purpose.
          </span>
          <span class="lang-de">
            Dir stehen bezüglich deiner bei Polar.sh oder über unsere Server erfassten Daten grundsätzlich die Rechte auf Auskunft,
            Berichtigung, Löschung, Einschränkung, Datenübertragbarkeit, Widerruf und Widerspruch zu. Wende dich hierzu an die im Impressum
            angegebene E-Mail-Adresse.
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <FooterSignature />

  <LangToggle />
</Layout>

<style>
  .privacy-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 5rem;
  }

  .privacy-card {
    background: #0d0e12b3;
    border: 1px solid #ffffff14;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px #00000080;
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }

  .privacy-card:hover {
    border-color: #8b7cf833;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(139, 124, 248, 0.05);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .card-label {
    font-family: monospace;
    color: #8b7cf8;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed #ffffff14;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .card-title {
    color: #ffffff;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .card-text {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .card-text:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .accent-link {
    color: #8b7cf8;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .accent-link:hover {
    color: #a99ef8;
  }

  /* Core Layout Styles override/additions */
  .bg-glow {
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(139, 124, 248, 0.08) 0%, rgba(8, 9, 11, 0) 70%);
    z-index: -2;
    pointer-events: none;
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    position: absolute;
  }
  .bg-glow-1 {
    top: -150px;
    left: calc(50% - 300px);
  }
  .bg-glow-2 {
    top: 600px;
    right: -200px;
  }
  .grid-overlay {
    background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
    z-index: -1;
    pointer-events: none;
    background-size: 80px 80px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
  }

  .tui-page-header {
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
  }
  .tui-logo {
    font-family: monospace;
    align-items: center;
    gap: .5rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: flex;
  }
  .logo-icon {
    color: #8b7cf8;
  }
  .logo-text {
    letter-spacing: -.03em;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 40%, #8b7cf8 100%);
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
  }
  .logo-blink {
    color: #8b7cf8;
    animation: 1s infinite cursor-blink;
  }
  @keyframes cursor-blink {
    0%, to { opacity: 0; }
    50% { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .tui-page-header-right {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }
  .back-link {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    font-family: monospace;
    border: 1px solid #ffffff14;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: .4rem .8rem;
    font-size: .85rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .back-link:hover {
    color: #8b7cf8;
    border-color: #8b7cf8;
    background: rgba(139, 124, 248, 0.05);
  }
  .lang-toggle-btn {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    color: #e2e8f0;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .lang-toggle-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(139, 124, 248, 0.15);
    border-color: rgba(139, 124, 248, 0.4);
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(139, 124, 248, 0.2);
  }

  .tui-page-main {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  }

  .tui-page-section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }
  .section-tag {
    font-family: monospace;
    letter-spacing: .12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #8b7cf8;
    background: rgba(139, 124, 248, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(139, 124, 248, 0.2);
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding: .3rem .8rem;
    font-size: .7rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading, inherit);
    color: #ffffff;
    letter-spacing: -.01em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    overflow-wrap: break-word;
  }
  .section-subtitle {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .lang-note {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
